<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٦٨٩٤ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5771">الْأَنْصَارِيُّ، </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1647">حُمَيْدٌ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/822">أَنَسٍ </a><span class="special">﵁</span>: <span class="c2">«أَنَّ ابْنَةَ النَّضْرِ لَطَمَتْ جَارِيَةً فَكَسَرَتْ ثَنِيَّتَهَا، فَأَتَوُا النَّبِيَّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> فَأَمَرَ بِالْقِصَاصِ.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>